  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of the effectiveness of vibroacoustic therapy in the complex treatment of acute
      respiratory failure
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Assessing the dynamics of changes in physical, instrumental and laboratory parameters in
      patients with acute respiratory failure taken in the study according to the inclusion
      criteria and comparing the results with the control group, studying the effectiveness of
      vibroacoustic lung therapy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
